line_1: Our Laird gets in his racked rents,
line_2: His coals, his kane, an' a' his stents:

line_1: His houshold charge, his annual rents,
Discounts your Notes, receives your Rents,
line_2: A Banker now, to all Intents.

line_1: No longer prey upon our annual rents,
line_2: Nor scare the nation with its big contents:
